Outstanding Shanghai Housing Loans Hit 15.2 Billion Yuan
SHANGHAI , December 24 ( Xinhua ) -- Outstanding housing loans to Shanghai residents stand at 15.2 billion yuan , according to a recent reports released by the Shanghai Branch of the People 's Bank of China ( PBOC ) , the central bank .
The outstanding volume includes loans of 8.19 billion yuan from the aggregate public fund and 7.01 billion yuan in commercial loans .
From January to November , commercial banks extended housing loans totalling 9.22 billion yuan , with outstanding loans accounting for 7.69 billion yuan of the total .
Projections indicate that some one million people have received loans during 1998 .
